ston_import: يجب عرضها على الحجر الصحي النباتي في أول منفذ حدودي  من أجل إجراء الكشف اللازم عليها وسحب العينات وفحصها وتأشير بياناتها من قبل فنيي وقاية النبات المفوضين في حال مطابقتها  لتعليمات  الحجر الصحي النباتي ، مع وجوب تقديم الشهادة الصحية النباتية الأصلية + صورة عن شهادة المنشأ مدون عليها عبارة(صورة طبق الأصل) أو (الأصل محفوظ لدينا)  ممهورة بخاتم الأمانة الجمركية المعنية + إذن الاستيراد الحجري + صورة عن بوليصة الشحن
ston_import_notes: يجب ان يكون اذن الاستيراد الحجري سابقاً لتاريخ إصدار الشهادة الصحية النباتية وشهادة المنشأ وبوليصة الشحن
ston_export: هذه المادة يجب عرضها  على فنيي وقاية النبات المفوضين (الحجر الصحي النباتي)في المنافذ الحدودية والأمانات الداخلية و المطارات والموانئ للكشف عليها  و سحب العينات وتأشير بياناتها بما يفيد مطابقتها  لتعليمات الحجر الصحي النباتي
ston_export_notes: تمنح شهادة صحية نباتية أصولاً ، مع التأكيد على مطابقة الإرسالية لمتطلبات الصحة النباتية في البلد المستورد إن قدمت من قبل صاحب العلاقة.
ston_export_en: This material must be presented to authorized plant protection technicians (plant quarantine) at border crossings, internal secretariats, airports, and ports to inspect it, withdraw samples, and mark their data to indicate their compliance with plant quarantine instructions.
ston_export_notes_en: A duly issued phytosanitary certificate is issued, confirming that the consignment conforms to the phytosanitary requirements of the importing country if submitted by the concerned party.
ston_import_en: It must be presented to the plant quarantine at the first border port in order to conduct the necessary examination on it, withdraw samples, examine it, and mark its data by authorized plant protection technicians if it conforms to the plant quarantine instructions. The original plant health certificate must be presented + a copy of the certificate of origin with the phrase written on it. (An exact copy) or (the original is kept with us) stamped with the stamp of the relevant customs secretariat + stone import permit + a copy of the bill of lading
ston_import_notes_en: The stone import permit must be prior to the date of issuance of the phytosanitary certificate, certificate of origin, and bill of lading

ston_export: هذه المادة يجب عرضها  على فنيي وقاية النبات المفوضين (الحجر الصحي النباتي)في المنافذ الحدودية والأمانات الداخلية و المطارات والموانئ للكشف عليها  و سحب العينات وتأشير بياناتها بما يفيد مطابقتها  لتعليمات الحجر الصحي النباتي
ston_export_notes: تمنح شهادة صحية نباتية أصولاً ، مع التأكيد على مطابقة الإرسالية لمتطلبات الصحة النباتية في البلد المستورد إن قدمت من قبل صاحب العلاقة.
ston_export_en: This material must be presented to authorized plant protection technicians (plant quarantine) at border crossings, internal secretariats, airports, and ports to inspect it, withdraw samples, and mark their data to indicate their compliance with plant quarantine instructions.
ston_export_notes_en: A duly issued phytosanitary certificate is issued, confirming that the consignment conforms to the phytosanitary requirements of the importing country if submitted by the concerned party.
ston_import_en: It must be presented to the plant quarantine at the first border port in order to conduct the necessary examination on it, withdraw samples, examine it, and mark its data by authorized plant protection technicians if it conforms to the plant quarantine instructions. The original plant health certificate must be presented + a copy of the certificate of origin with the phrase written on it. (An exact copy) or (the original is kept with us) stamped with the stamp of the relevant customs secretariat + stone import permit + a copy of the bill of lading
ston_import_notes_en: The stone import permit must be prior to the date of issuance of the phytosanitary certificate, certificate of origin, and bill of lading

ston_export: هذه المادة يجب عرضها  على فنيي وقاية النبات المفوضين (الحجر الصحي النباتي)في المنافذ الحدودية والأمانات الداخلية و المطارات والموانئ للكشف عليها  و سحب العينات وتأشير بياناتها بما يفيد مطابقتها  لتعليمات الحجر الصحي النباتي
ston_export_notes: تمنح شهادة صحية نباتية أصولاً ، مع التأكيد على مطابقة الإرسالية لمتطلبات الصحة النباتية في البلد المستورد إن قدمت من قبل صاحب العلاقة.
ston_export_en: This material must be presented to authorized plant protection technicians (plant quarantine) at border crossings, internal secretariats, airports, and ports to inspect it, withdraw samples, and mark their data to indicate their compliance with plant quarantine instructions.
ston_export_notes_en: A duly issued phytosanitary certificate is issued, confirming that the consignment conforms to the phytosanitary requirements of the importing country if submitted by the concerned party.
ston_import_en: It must be presented to the plant quarantine at the first border port in order to conduct the necessary examination on it, withdraw samples, examine it, and mark its data by authorized plant protection technicians if it conforms to the plant quarantine instructions. The original plant health certificate must be presented + a copy of the certificate of origin with the phrase written on it. (An exact copy) or (the original is kept with us) stamped with the stamp of the relevant customs secretariat + stone import permit + a copy of the bill of lading
ston_import_notes_en: The stone import permit must be prior to the date of issuance of the phytosanitary certificate, certificate of origin, and bill of lading

ston_export: هذه المادة يجب عرضها  على فنيي وقاية النبات المفوضين (الحجر الصحي النباتي)في المنافذ الحدودية والأمانات الداخلية و المطارات والموانئ للكشف عليها  و سحب العينات وتأشير بياناتها بما يفيد مطابقتها  لتعليمات الحجر الصحي النباتي
ston_export_notes: تمنح شهادة صحية نباتية أصولاً ، مع التأكيد على مطابقة الإرسالية لمتطلبات الصحة النباتية في البلد المستورد إن قدمت من قبل صاحب العلاقة.
ston_export_en: This material must be presented to authorized plant protection technicians (plant quarantine) at border crossings, internal secretariats, airports, and ports to inspect it, withdraw samples, and mark their data to indicate their compliance with plant quarantine instructions.
ston_export_notes_en: A duly issued phytosanitary certificate is issued, confirming that the consignment conforms to the phytosanitary requirements of the importing country if submitted by the concerned party.
ston_import_en: It must be presented to the plant quarantine at the first border port in order to conduct the necessary examination on it, withdraw samples, examine it, and mark its data by authorized plant protection technicians if it conforms to the plant quarantine instructions. The original plant health certificate must be presented + a copy of the certificate of origin with the phrase written on it. (An exact copy) or (the original is kept with us) stamped with the stamp of the relevant customs secretariat + stone import permit + a copy of the bill of lading
ston_import_notes_en: The stone import permit must be prior to the date of issuance of the phytosanitary certificate, certificate of origin, and bill of lading

ston_export: هذه المادة يجب عرضها  على فنيي وقاية النبات المفوضين (الحجر الصحي النباتي)في المنافذ الحدودية والأمانات الداخلية و المطارات والموانئ للكشف عليها  و سحب العينات وتأشير بياناتها بما يفيد مطابقتها  لتعليمات الحجر الصحي النباتي
ston_export_notes: تمنح شهادة صحية نباتية أصولاً ، مع التأكيد على مطابقة الإرسالية لمتطلبات الصحة النباتية في البلد المستورد إن قدمت من قبل صاحب العلاقة.
ston_export_en: This material must be presented to authorized plant protection technicians (plant quarantine) at border crossings, internal secretariats, airports, and ports to inspect it, withdraw samples, and mark their data to indicate their compliance with plant quarantine instructions.
ston_export_notes_en: A duly issued phytosanitary certificate is issued, confirming that the consignment conforms to the phytosanitary requirements of the importing country if submitted by the concerned party.
ston_import_en: It must be presented to the plant quarantine at the first border port in order to conduct the necessary examination on it, withdraw samples, examine it, and mark its data by authorized plant protection technicians if it conforms to the plant quarantine instructions. The original plant health certificate must be presented + a copy of the certificate of origin with the phrase written on it. (An exact copy) or (the original is kept with us) stamped with the stamp of the relevant customs secretariat + stone import permit + a copy of the bill of lading
ston_import_notes_en: The stone import permit must be prior to the date of issuance of the phytosanitary certificate, certificate of origin, and bill of lading

ston_export: هذه المادة يجب عرضها  على فنيي وقاية النبات المفوضين (الحجر الصحي النباتي)في المنافذ الحدودية والأمانات الداخلية و المطارات والموانئ للكشف عليها  و سحب العينات وتأشير بياناتها بما يفيد مطابقتها  لتعليمات الحجر الصحي النباتي
ston_export_notes: تمنح شهادة صحية نباتية أصولاً ، مع التأكيد على مطابقة الإرسالية لمتطلبات الصحة النباتية في البلد المستورد إن قدمت من قبل صاحب العلاقة.
ston_export_en: This material must be presented to authorized plant protection technicians (plant quarantine) at border crossings, internal secretariats, airports, and ports to inspect it, withdraw samples, and mark their data to indicate their compliance with plant quarantine instructions.
ston_export_notes_en: A duly issued phytosanitary certificate is issued, confirming that the consignment conforms to the phytosanitary requirements of the importing country if submitted by the concerned party.
ston_import_en: It must be presented to the plant quarantine at the first border port in order to conduct the necessary examination on it, withdraw samples, examine it, and mark its data by authorized plant protection technicians if it conforms to the plant quarantine instructions. The original plant health certificate must be presented + a copy of the certificate of origin with the phrase written on it. (An exact copy) or (the original is kept with us) stamped with the stamp of the relevant customs secretariat + stone import permit + a copy of the bill of lading
ston_import_notes_en: The stone import permit must be prior to the date of issuance of the phytosanitary certificate, certificate of origin, and bill of lading

ston_export: هذه المادة يجب عرضها  على فنيي وقاية النبات المفوضين (الحجر الصحي النباتي)في المنافذ الحدودية والأمانات الداخلية و المطارات والموانئ للكشف عليها  و سحب العينات وتأشير بياناتها بما يفيد مطابقتها  لتعليمات الحجر الصحي النباتي
ston_export_notes: تمنح شهادة صحية نباتية أصولاً ، مع التأكيد على مطابقة الإرسالية لمتطلبات الصحة النباتية في البلد المستورد إن قدمت من قبل صاحب العلاقة.
ston_export_en: This material must be presented to authorized plant protection technicians (plant quarantine) at border crossings, internal secretariats, airports, and ports to inspect it, withdraw samples, and mark their data to indicate their compliance with plant quarantine instructions.
ston_export_notes_en: A duly issued phytosanitary certificate is issued, confirming that the consignment conforms to the phytosanitary requirements of the importing country if submitted by the concerned party.
ston_import_en: It must be presented to the plant quarantine at the first border port in order to conduct the necessary examination on it, withdraw samples, examine it, and mark its data by authorized plant protection technicians if it conforms to the plant quarantine instructions. The original plant health certificate must be presented + a copy of the certificate of origin with the phrase written on it. (An exact copy) or (the original is kept with us) stamped with the stamp of the relevant customs secretariat + stone import permit + a copy of the bill of lading
ston_import_notes_en: The stone import permit must be prior to the date of issuance of the phytosanitary certificate, certificate of origin, and bill of lading

ston_export: هذه المادة يجب عرضها  على فنيي وقاية النبات المفوضين (الحجر الصحي النباتي)في المنافذ الحدودية والأمانات الداخلية و المطارات والموانئ للكشف عليها  و سحب العينات وتأشير بياناتها بما يفيد مطابقتها  لتعليمات الحجر الصحي النباتي
ston_export_notes: تمنح شهادة صحية نباتية أصولاً ، مع التأكيد على مطابقة الإرسالية لمتطلبات الصحة النباتية في البلد المستورد إن قدمت من قبل صاحب العلاقة.
ston_export_en: This material must be presented to authorized plant protection technicians (plant quarantine) at border crossings, internal secretariats, airports, and ports to inspect it, withdraw samples, and mark their data to indicate their compliance with plant quarantine instructions.
ston_export_notes_en: A duly issued phytosanitary certificate is issued, confirming that the consignment conforms to the phytosanitary requirements of the importing country if submitted by the concerned party.
ston_import_en: It must be presented to the plant quarantine at the first border port in order to conduct the necessary examination on it, withdraw samples, examine it, and mark its data by authorized plant protection technicians if it conforms to the plant quarantine instructions. The original plant health certificate must be presented + a copy of the certificate of origin with the phrase written on it. (An exact copy) or (the original is kept with us) stamped with the stamp of the relevant customs secretariat + stone import permit + a copy of the bill of lading
ston_import_notes_en: The stone import permit must be prior to the date of issuance of the phytosanitary certificate, certificate of origin, and bill of lading

ston_export: هذه المادة يجب عرضها  على فنيي وقاية النبات المفوضين (الحجر الصحي النباتي)في المنافذ الحدودية والأمانات الداخلية و المطارات والموانئ للكشف عليها  و سحب العينات وتأشير بياناتها بما يفيد مطابقتها  لتعليمات الحجر الصحي النباتي
ston_export_notes: تمنح شهادة صحية نباتية أصولاً ، مع التأكيد على مطابقة الإرسالية لمتطلبات الصحة النباتية في البلد المستورد إن قدمت من قبل صاحب العلاقة.
ston_export_en: This material must be presented to authorized plant protection technicians (plant quarantine) at border crossings, internal secretariats, airports, and ports to inspect it, withdraw samples, and mark their data to indicate their compliance with plant quarantine instructions.
ston_export_notes_en: A duly issued phytosanitary certificate is issued, confirming that the consignment conforms to the phytosanitary requirements of the importing country if submitted by the concerned party.
ston_import_en: It must be presented to the plant quarantine at the first border port in order to conduct the necessary examination on it, withdraw samples, examine it, and mark its data by authorized plant protection technicians if it conforms to the plant quarantine instructions. The original plant health certificate must be presented + a copy of the certificate of origin with the phrase written on it. (An exact copy) or (the original is kept with us) stamped with the stamp of the relevant customs secretariat + stone import permit + a copy of the bill of lading
ston_import_notes_en: The stone import permit must be prior to the date of issuance of the phytosanitary certificate, certificate of origin, and bill of lading

ston_export: هذه المادة يجب عرضها  على فنيي وقاية النبات المفوضين (الحجر الصحي النباتي)في المنافذ الحدودية والأمانات الداخلية و المطارات والموانئ للكشف عليها  و سحب العينات وتأشير بياناتها بما يفيد مطابقتها  لتعليمات الحجر الصحي النباتي
ston_export_notes: تمنح شهادة صحية نباتية أصولاً ، مع التأكيد على مطابقة الإرسالية لمتطلبات الصحة النباتية في البلد المستورد إن قدمت من قبل صاحب العلاقة.
ston_export_en: This material must be presented to authorized plant protection technicians (plant quarantine) at border crossings, internal secretariats, airports, and ports to inspect it, withdraw samples, and mark their data to indicate their compliance with plant quarantine instructions.
ston_export_notes_en: A duly issued phytosanitary certificate is issued, confirming that the consignment conforms to the phytosanitary requirements of the importing country if submitted by the concerned party.
ston_import_en: It must be presented to the plant quarantine at the first border port in order to conduct the necessary examination on it, withdraw samples, examine it, and mark its data by authorized plant protection technicians if it conforms to the plant quarantine instructions. The original plant health certificate must be presented + a copy of the certificate of origin with the phrase written on it. (An exact copy) or (the original is kept with us) stamped with the stamp of the relevant customs secretariat + stone import permit + a copy of the bill of lading
ston_import_notes_en: The stone import permit must be prior to the date of issuance of the phytosanitary certificate, certificate of origin, and bill of lading

ston_export: هذه المادة يجب عرضها  على فنيي وقاية النبات المفوضين (الحجر الصحي النباتي)في المنافذ الحدودية والأمانات الداخلية و المطارات والموانئ للكشف عليها  و سحب العينات وتأشير بياناتها بما يفيد مطابقتها  لتعليمات الحجر الصحي النباتي
ston_export_notes: تمنح شهادة صحية نباتية أصولاً ، مع التأكيد على مطابقة الإرسالية لمتطلبات الصحة النباتية في البلد المستورد إن قدمت من قبل صاحب العلاقة.
ston_export_en: This material must be presented to authorized plant protection technicians (plant quarantine) at border crossings, internal secretariats, airports, and ports to inspect it, withdraw samples, and mark their data to indicate their compliance with plant quarantine instructions.
ston_export_notes_en: A duly issued phytosanitary certificate is issued, confirming that the consignment conforms to the phytosanitary requirements of the importing country if submitted by the concerned party.
ston_import_en: It must be presented to the plant quarantine at the first border port in order to conduct the necessary examination on it, withdraw samples, examine it, and mark its data by authorized plant protection technicians if it conforms to the plant quarantine instructions. The original plant health certificate must be presented + a copy of the certificate of origin with the phrase written on it. (An exact copy) or (the original is kept with us) stamped with the stamp of the relevant customs secretariat + stone import permit + a copy of the bill of lading
ston_import_notes_en: The stone import permit must be prior to the date of issuance of the phytosanitary certificate, certificate of origin, and bill of lading

ston_export: هذه المادة يجب عرضها  على فنيي وقاية النبات المفوضين (الحجر الصحي النباتي)في المنافذ الحدودية والأمانات الداخلية و المطارات والموانئ للكشف عليها  و سحب العينات وتأشير بياناتها بما يفيد مطابقتها  لتعليمات الحجر الصحي النباتي
ston_export_notes: تمنح شهادة صحية نباتية أصولاً ، مع التأكيد على مطابقة الإرسالية لمتطلبات الصحة النباتية في البلد المستورد إن قدمت من قبل صاحب العلاقة.
ston_export_en: This material must be presented to authorized plant protection technicians (plant quarantine) at border crossings, internal secretariats, airports, and ports to inspect it, withdraw samples, and mark their data to indicate their compliance with plant quarantine instructions.
ston_export_notes_en: A duly issued phytosanitary certificate is issued, confirming that the consignment conforms to the phytosanitary requirements of the importing country if submitted by the concerned party.
ston_import_en: It must be presented to the plant quarantine at the first border port in order to conduct the necessary examination on it, withdraw samples, examine it, and mark its data by authorized plant protection technicians if it conforms to the plant quarantine instructions. The original plant health certificate must be presented + a copy of the certificate of origin with the phrase written on it. (An exact copy) or (the original is kept with us) stamped with the stamp of the relevant customs secretariat + stone import permit + a copy of the bill of lading
ston_import_notes_en: The stone import permit must be prior to the date of issuance of the phytosanitary certificate, certificate of origin, and bill of lading

ston_export: هذه المادة يجب عرضها  على فنيي وقاية النبات المفوضين (الحجر الصحي النباتي)في المنافذ الحدودية والأمانات الداخلية و المطارات والموانئ للكشف عليها  و سحب العينات وتأشير بياناتها بما يفيد مطابقتها  لتعليمات الحجر الصحي النباتي
ston_export_notes: تمنح شهادة صحية نباتية أصولاً ، مع التأكيد على مطابقة الإرسالية لمتطلبات الصحة النباتية في البلد المستورد إن قدمت من قبل صاحب العلاقة.
ston_export_en: This material must be presented to authorized plant protection technicians (plant quarantine) at border crossings, internal secretariats, airports, and ports to inspect it, withdraw samples, and mark their data to indicate their compliance with plant quarantine instructions.
ston_export_notes_en: A duly issued phytosanitary certificate is issued, confirming that the consignment conforms to the phytosanitary requirements of the importing country if submitted by the concerned party.
ston_import_en: It must be presented to the plant quarantine at the first border port in order to conduct the necessary examination on it, withdraw samples, examine it, and mark its data by authorized plant protection technicians if it conforms to the plant quarantine instructions. The original plant health certificate must be presented + a copy of the certificate of origin with the phrase written on it. (An exact copy) or (the original is kept with us) stamped with the stamp of the relevant customs secretariat + stone import permit + a copy of the bill of lading
ston_import_notes_en: The stone import permit must be prior to the date of issuance of the phytosanitary certificate, certificate of origin, and bill of lading

ston_export: هذه المادة يجب عرضها  على فنيي وقاية النبات المفوضين (الحجر الصحي النباتي)في المنافذ الحدودية والأمانات الداخلية و المطارات والموانئ للكشف عليها  و سحب العينات وتأشير بياناتها بما يفيد مطابقتها  لتعليمات الحجر الصحي النباتي
ston_export_notes: تمنح شهادة صحية نباتية أصولاً ، مع التأكيد على مطابقة الإرسالية لمتطلبات الصحة النباتية في البلد المستورد إن قدمت من قبل صاحب العلاقة.
ston_export_en: This material must be presented to authorized plant protection technicians (plant quarantine) at border crossings, internal secretariats, airports, and ports to inspect it, withdraw samples, and mark their data to indicate their compliance with plant quarantine instructions.
ston_export_notes_en: A duly issued phytosanitary certificate is issued, confirming that the consignment conforms to the phytosanitary requirements of the importing country if submitted by the concerned party.
ston_import_en: It must be presented to the plant quarantine at the first border port in order to conduct the necessary examination on it, withdraw samples, examine it, and mark its data by authorized plant protection technicians if it conforms to the plant quarantine instructions. The original plant health certificate must be presented + a copy of the certificate of origin with the phrase written on it. (An exact copy) or (the original is kept with us) stamped with the stamp of the relevant customs secretariat + stone import permit + a copy of the bill of lading
ston_import_notes_en: The stone import permit must be prior to the date of issuance of the phytosanitary certificate, certificate of origin, and bill of lading

ston_export: هذه المادة يجب عرضها  على فنيي وقاية النبات المفوضين (الحجر الصحي النباتي)في المنافذ الحدودية والأمانات الداخلية و المطارات والموانئ للكشف عليها  و سحب العينات وتأشير بياناتها بما يفيد مطابقتها  لتعليمات الحجر الصحي النباتي
ston_export_notes: تمنح شهادة صحية نباتية أصولاً ، مع التأكيد على مطابقة الإرسالية لمتطلبات الصحة النباتية في البلد المستورد إن قدمت من قبل صاحب العلاقة.
ston_export_en: This material must be presented to authorized plant protection technicians (plant quarantine) at border crossings, internal secretariats, airports, and ports to inspect it, withdraw samples, and mark their data to indicate their compliance with plant quarantine instructions.
ston_export_notes_en: A duly issued phytosanitary certificate is issued, confirming that the consignment conforms to the phytosanitary requirements of the importing country if submitted by the concerned party.
ston_import_en: It must be presented to the plant quarantine at the first border port in order to conduct the necessary examination on it, withdraw samples, examine it, and mark its data by authorized plant protection technicians if it conforms to the plant quarantine instructions. The original plant health certificate must be presented + a copy of the certificate of origin with the phrase written on it. (An exact copy) or (the original is kept with us) stamped with the stamp of the relevant customs secretariat + stone import permit + a copy of the bill of lading
ston_import_notes_en: The stone import permit must be prior to the date of issuance of the phytosanitary certificate, certificate of origin, and bill of lading

ston_export: هذه المادة يجب عرضها  على فنيي وقاية النبات المفوضين (الحجر الصحي النباتي)في المنافذ الحدودية والأمانات الداخلية و المطارات والموانئ للكشف عليها  و سحب العينات وتأشير بياناتها بما يفيد مطابقتها  لتعليمات الحجر الصحي النباتي
ston_export_notes: تمنح شهادة صحية نباتية أصولاً ، مع التأكيد على مطابقة الإرسالية لمتطلبات الصحة النباتية في البلد المستورد إن قدمت من قبل صاحب العلاقة.
ston_export_en: This material must be presented to authorized plant protection technicians (plant quarantine) at border crossings, internal secretariats, airports, and ports to inspect it, withdraw samples, and mark their data to indicate their compliance with plant quarantine instructions.
ston_export_notes_en: A duly issued phytosanitary certificate is issued, confirming that the consignment conforms to the phytosanitary requirements of the importing country if submitted by the concerned party.
ston_import_en: It must be presented to the plant quarantine at the first border port in order to conduct the necessary examination on it, withdraw samples, examine it, and mark its data by authorized plant protection technicians if it conforms to the plant quarantine instructions. The original plant health certificate must be presented + a copy of the certificate of origin with the phrase written on it. (An exact copy) or (the original is kept with us) stamped with the stamp of the relevant customs secretariat + stone import permit + a copy of the bill of lading
ston_import_notes_en: The stone import permit must be prior to the date of issuance of the phytosanitary certificate, certificate of origin, and bill of lading

ston_export: هذه المادة يجب عرضها  على فنيي وقاية النبات المفوضين (الحجر الصحي النباتي)في المنافذ الحدودية والأمانات الداخلية و المطارات والموانئ للكشف عليها  و سحب العينات وتأشير بياناتها بما يفيد مطابقتها  لتعليمات الحجر الصحي النباتي
ston_export_notes: تمنح شهادة صحية نباتية أصولاً ، مع التأكيد على مطابقة الإرسالية لمتطلبات الصحة النباتية في البلد المستورد إن قدمت من قبل صاحب العلاقة.
ston_export_en: This material must be presented to authorized plant protection technicians (plant quarantine) at border crossings, internal secretariats, airports, and ports to inspect it, withdraw samples, and mark their data to indicate their compliance with plant quarantine instructions.
ston_export_notes_en: A duly issued phytosanitary certificate is issued, confirming that the consignment conforms to the phytosanitary requirements of the importing country if submitted by the concerned party.
ston_import_en: It must be presented to the plant quarantine at the first border port in order to conduct the necessary examination on it, withdraw samples, examine it, and mark its data by authorized plant protection technicians if it conforms to the plant quarantine instructions. The original plant health certificate must be presented + a copy of the certificate of origin with the phrase written on it. (An exact copy) or (the original is kept with us) stamped with the stamp of the relevant customs secretariat + stone import permit + a copy of the bill of lading
ston_import_notes_en: The stone import permit must be prior to the date of issuance of the phytosanitary certificate, certificate of origin, and bill of lading

ston_export: هذه المادة يجب عرضها  على فنيي وقاية النبات المفوضين (الحجر الصحي النباتي)في المنافذ الحدودية والأمانات الداخلية و المطارات والموانئ للكشف عليها  و سحب العينات وتأشير بياناتها بما يفيد مطابقتها  لتعليمات الحجر الصحي النباتي
ston_export_notes: تمنح شهادة صحية نباتية أصولاً ، مع التأكيد على مطابقة الإرسالية لمتطلبات الصحة النباتية في البلد المستورد إن قدمت من قبل صاحب العلاقة.
ston_export_en: This material must be presented to authorized plant protection technicians (plant quarantine) at border crossings, internal secretariats, airports, and ports to inspect it, withdraw samples, and mark their data to indicate their compliance with plant quarantine instructions.
ston_export_notes_en: A duly issued phytosanitary certificate is issued, confirming that the consignment conforms to the phytosanitary requirements of the importing country if submitted by the concerned party.
ston_import_en: It must be presented to the plant quarantine at the first border port in order to conduct the necessary examination on it, withdraw samples, examine it, and mark its data by authorized plant protection technicians if it conforms to the plant quarantine instructions. The original plant health certificate must be presented + a copy of the certificate of origin with the phrase written on it. (An exact copy) or (the original is kept with us) stamped with the stamp of the relevant customs secretariat + stone import permit + a copy of the bill of lading
ston_import_notes_en: The stone import permit must be prior to the date of issuance of the phytosanitary certificate, certificate of origin, and bill of lading

ston_export: هذه المادة يجب عرضها  على فنيي وقاية النبات المفوضين (الحجر الصحي النباتي)في المنافذ الحدودية والأمانات الداخلية و المطارات والموانئ للكشف عليها  و سحب العينات وتأشير بياناتها بما يفيد مطابقتها  لتعليمات الحجر الصحي النباتي
ston_export_notes: تمنح شهادة صحية نباتية أصولاً ، مع التأكيد على مطابقة الإرسالية لمتطلبات الصحة النباتية في البلد المستورد إن قدمت من قبل صاحب العلاقة.
ston_export_en: This material must be presented to authorized plant protection technicians (plant quarantine) at border crossings, internal secretariats, airports, and ports to inspect it, withdraw samples, and mark their data to indicate their compliance with plant quarantine instructions.
ston_export_notes_en: A duly issued phytosanitary certificate is issued, confirming that the consignment conforms to the phytosanitary requirements of the importing country if submitted by the concerned party.
ston_import_en: It must be presented to the plant quarantine at the first border port in order to conduct the necessary examination on it, withdraw samples, examine it, and mark its data by authorized plant protection technicians if it conforms to the plant quarantine instructions. The original plant health certificate must be presented + a copy of the certificate of origin with the phrase written on it. (An exact copy) or (the original is kept with us) stamped with the stamp of the relevant customs secretariat + stone import permit + a copy of the bill of lading
ston_import_notes_en: The stone import permit must be prior to the date of issuance of the phytosanitary certificate, certificate of origin, and bill of lading

ston_export: هذه المادة يجب عرضها  على فنيي وقاية النبات المفوضين (الحجر الصحي النباتي)في المنافذ الحدودية والأمانات الداخلية و المطارات والموانئ للكشف عليها  و سحب العينات وتأشير بياناتها بما يفيد مطابقتها  لتعليمات الحجر الصحي النباتي
ston_export_notes: تمنح شهادة صحية نباتية أصولاً ، مع التأكيد على مطابقة الإرسالية لمتطلبات الصحة النباتية في البلد المستورد إن قدمت من قبل صاحب العلاقة.
ston_export_en: This material must be presented to authorized plant protection technicians (plant quarantine) at border crossings, internal secretariats, airports, and ports to inspect it, withdraw samples, and mark their data to indicate their compliance with plant quarantine instructions.
ston_export_notes_en: A duly issued phytosanitary certificate is issued, confirming that the consignment conforms to the phytosanitary requirements of the importing country if submitted by the concerned party.
ston_import_en: It must be presented to the plant quarantine at the first border port in order to conduct the necessary examination on it, withdraw samples, examine it, and mark its data by authorized plant protection technicians if it conforms to the plant quarantine instructions. The original plant health certificate must be presented + a copy of the certificate of origin with the phrase written on it. (An exact copy) or (the original is kept with us) stamped with the stamp of the relevant customs secretariat + stone import permit + a copy of the bill of lading
ston_import_notes_en: The stone import permit must be prior to the date of issuance of the phytosanitary certificate, certificate of origin, and bill of lading

ston_export: هذه المادة يجب عرضها  على فنيي وقاية النبات المفوضين (الحجر الصحي النباتي)في المنافذ الحدودية والأمانات الداخلية و المطارات والموانئ للكشف عليها  و سحب العينات وتأشير بياناتها بما يفيد مطابقتها  لتعليمات الحجر الصحي النباتي
ston_export_notes: تمنح شهادة صحية نباتية أصولاً ، مع التأكيد على مطابقة الإرسالية لمتطلبات الصحة النباتية في البلد المستورد إن قدمت من قبل صاحب العلاقة.
ston_export_en: This material must be presented to authorized plant protection technicians (plant quarantine) at border crossings, internal secretariats, airports, and ports to inspect it, withdraw samples, and mark their data to indicate their compliance with plant quarantine instructions.
ston_export_notes_en: A duly issued phytosanitary certificate is issued, confirming that the consignment conforms to the phytosanitary requirements of the importing country if submitted by the concerned party.
ston_import_en: It must be presented to the plant quarantine at the first border port in order to conduct the necessary examination on it, withdraw samples, examine it, and mark its data by authorized plant protection technicians if it conforms to the plant quarantine instructions. The original plant health certificate must be presented + a copy of the certificate of origin with the phrase written on it. (An exact copy) or (the original is kept with us) stamped with the stamp of the relevant customs secretariat + stone import permit + a copy of the bill of lading
ston_import_notes_en: The stone import permit must be prior to the date of issuance of the phytosanitary certificate, certificate of origin, and bill of lading

ston_export: هذه المادة يجب عرضها  على فنيي وقاية النبات المفوضين (الحجر الصحي النباتي)في المنافذ الحدودية والأمانات الداخلية و المطارات والموانئ للكشف عليها  و سحب العينات وتأشير بياناتها بما يفيد مطابقتها  لتعليمات الحجر الصحي النباتي

ston_export_notes_en: A duly issued phytosanitary certificate is issued, confirming that the consignment conforms to the phytosanitary requirements of the importing country if submitted by the concerned party.
ston_import_en: It must be presented to the plant quarantine at the first border port in order to conduct the necessary examination on it, withdraw samples, examine it, and mark its data by authorized plant protection technicians if it conforms to the plant quarantine instructions. The original plant health certificate must be presented + a copy of the certificate of origin with the phrase written on it. (An exact copy) or (the original is kept with us) stamped with the stamp of the relevant customs secretariat + stone import permit + a copy of the bill of lading
ston_import_notes_en: The stone import permit must be prior to the date of issuance of the phytosanitary certificate, certificate of origin, and bill of lading

ston_export_en: This material must be presented to authorized plant protection technicians (plant quarantine) at border crossings, internal secretariats, airports, and ports to inspect it, withdraw samples, and mark their data to indicate their compliance with plant quarantine instructions.

ston_export: هذه المادة يجب عرضها  على فنيي وقاية النبات المفوضين (الحجر الصحي النباتي)في المنافذ الحدودية والأمانات الداخلية و المطارات والموانئ للكشف عليها  و سحب العينات وتأشير بياناتها بما يفيد مطابقتها  لتعليمات الحجر الصحي النباتي

ston_export_en: This material must be presented to authorized plant protection technicians (plant quarantine) at border crossings, internal secretariats, airports, and ports to inspect it, withdraw samples, and mark their data to indicate their compliance with plant quarantine instructions.

ston_import_en: It must be presented to the plant quarantine at the first border port in order to conduct the necessary examination on it, withdraw samples, examine it, and mark its data by authorized plant protection technicians if it conforms to the plant quarantine instructions. (An exact copy) or (the original is kept with us) stamped with the stamp of the relevant customs secretariat + stone import permit + a copy of the bill of lading
ston_import_notes_en: The stone import permit must be prior to the date of issuance of the phytosanitary certificate, certificate of origin, and bill of lading

ston_export_en: This material must be presented to authorized plant protection technicians (plant quarantine) at border crossings, internal secretariats, airports, and ports to inspect it, withdraw samples, and mark their data to indicate their compliance with plant quarantine instructions.
ston_export_notes_en: A phytosanitary certificate is granted based on a request submitted by the concerned party to the duly concerned plant quarantine center, with confirmation that the consignment conforms to the phytosanitary requirements of the importing country if submitted by the concerned party.
ston_import_en: It must be presented to the plant quarantine at the first border port in order to conduct the necessary examination on it, withdraw samples, examine it, and record its data by authorized plant protection technicians if it conforms to the plant quarantine instructions. A copy of the documents attached to the consignment must be provided without specifying them, and all their data must be recorded in records. Specially designed by the Plant Quarantine Center.

ston_import:
أن تكون الإرسالية حطب جاف ومنزوع القلف ( اللحاء) وبغرض التدفئة حصراً.
يتم الكشف اللازم على الإرسالية في منفذ الدخول وسحب عينات ممثلة للإرسالية والـتأكد من مطابقتها لتعليمات الحجر الصحي النباتي النافذة.
ston_import_notes:
الحصول على إذن استيراد حصري مسبق من قبل مديرية وقاية النبات وبعد تقديم صاحب العلاقة  الطلب اللازم أصولاً.
 أن ترفق الإرسالية بشهادة صحية نباتية أصلية من البلد المصدر تثبت خلوها من الأفات النباتية وأن يثبت في بند المعاملة أنه تم معاملة الإرسالية على درجة حرارة لا تقل عن 56 درجة مئوية لمدة لا تقل عن 30 دقيقة أو أي طريقة أخرى مثبت أنها فعالة في القضاء على الآفات النباتية ، أو إرفاق الإرسالية بشهادة تعقيم تثبت ذلك ، ويجب أن لا يزيد أطوال الأخشاب المستوردة عن 50 سم  ولا تزيد سماكتها عن 30 سم لضمان فعالية عملية التعقيم.
ston_export: هذه المادة يجب عرضها على فنيي وقاية النبات المفوضين (الحجر الصحي النباتي)في المنافذ الحدودية والأمانات الداخلية و المطارات والموانئ للكشف عليها و سحب العينات وتأشير بياناتها بما يفيد مطابقتها لتعليمات الحجر الصحي النباتي
ston_export_notes: تمنح شهادة صحية نباتية أصولاً ، مع التأكيد على مطابقة الإرسالية لمتطلبات الصحة النباتية في البلد المستورد إن قدمت من قبل صاحب العلاقة.
ston_export_en: This material must be presented to authorized plant protection technicians (plant quarantine) at border crossings, internal secretariats, airports, and ports to inspect it, withdraw samples, and mark their data to indicate their compliance with plant quarantine instructions.
ston_export_notes_en: A duly issued phytosanitary certificate is issued, confirming that the consignment conforms to the phytosanitary requirements of the importing country if submitted by the concerned party.
ston_import_en:
The consignment  must be dry firewood with bark removed, intended for heating purposes only.
Necessary inspection will be conducted at the entry point, and representative samples will be taken to ensure compliance with the prevailing phytosanitary regulations.
ston_import_notes_en:
Obtaining prior exclusive import permission from the Plant Protection Directorate, after submitting the necessary request by the concerned party. 
The consignment must be accompanied by an original phytosanitary certificate from the exporting country confirming its freedom from plant pests. It must be stated in the treatment section that the consignment  has been treated at a temperature of not less than 56 degrees Celsius for at least 30 minutes, or by any other method proven to be effective in controlling plant pests. Alternatively, the consignment  must be accompanied by a sterilization certificate confirming this. The imported wood lengths should not exceed 50 cm and the thickness should not exceed 30 cm to ensure the effectiveness of the sterilization process.
